154
00:05:37.865 --> 00:05:38.505
añadió,

155
00:05:38.905 --> 00:05:39.705
sí,

156
00:05:40.025 --> 00:05:40.825
está bien,

157
00:05:41.385 --> 00:05:42.265
basta con esto,

158
00:05:43.490 --> 00:05:46.050
