199
00:07:25.645 --> 00:07:27.885
No hay prisa, no hay prisa.

200
00:07:28.365 --> 00:07:29.565
¿Fuma usted?

201
00:07:29.965 --> 00:07:31.485
Tome un cigarrillo,

202
00:07:31.805 --> 00:07:34.125
